This is a great package tracking app! I really like the tracking details and the package status change notifications. Loading your packages it is pretty simple. However the one drawback is that you have to manually select the carrier from a list when adding your package. This should be automatically generated by the app, since all carriers have a unique tracking number. Foe example, a UPS tracking number, for domestic packages within the USA, will usually start with "1Z". DHL Express supports the carrier-independent ISO standard 15459-1¬†for the identification of single packages....and so on. For this reason I could only give the app 4 stars
